{"word":"Thessalonica","slug":"thessalonica","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Thessalonica</b> A city of Macedonia.<br/> Paul visits<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=1'>Act 17:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=4&verse=16'>Phi 4:16</a><br/> People of, persecute Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=8'>Act 17:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=11'>Act 17:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=13'>Act 17:13</a><br/> Men of, accompany Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=20&verse=4'>Act 20:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=27&verse=2'>Act 27:2</a><br/> Paul writes to Christians in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=1&verse=1'>1Th 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=53&chapter=1&verse=1'>2Th 1:1</a><br/> Demas goes to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=10'>2Ti 4:10</a>"}]}